100:    2   4   5   10  20  25  50  100

if 100 is divisible by 2, say 2
if 100 is divisible by 3, say 3
if 100 is divisible by 4, say 4
if 100 is divisible by 5, say 5

Greatest Divisor of any number - Same Number: 

int no = 100;
int div = 2; 
while(div<=no)
{
if(no%div == 0)
{
System.out.print(div+" "); 
}
div = div + 1; 
}




